Dialogue: 5,0:00:37.30,0:00:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Your dad's a gang boss?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:40.68,0:00:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're the heir to a yakuza syndicate?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the boss of the Beehive gangster outfit.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:48.23,0:00:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ardelt Kirisaki-Wagner and his daughter, Miss Kirisaki Chitoge!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:52.94,0:00:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard all about you from your father.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:56.78,0:00:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great to finally meet you, Raku-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:58.45,0:00:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:59.62,0:01:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never getting together with this guy! Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:01.66,0:01:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Dad! It'll never work out with a maniac like her!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:04.46,0:01:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great and all, but it's the only way we can prevent this war.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:09.59,0:01:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:13.72,0:01:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:14.97,0:01:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:21.14,0:01:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found you, Mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:23.22,0:01:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's true. These Shuei-gumi rats really did kidnap you!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:27.69,0:01:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Claude!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:29.44,0:01:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear not, Mistress.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:31.77,0:01:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As an executive leader of the beehive, your protection is my highest priority!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:36.28,0:01:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore I've taken it upon myself to come rescue you!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:45.20,0:01:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, if it isn't one of the Beehive's top dogs!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:48.75,0:01:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don'tcha think you're way outta line?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:52.05,0:01:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been goin' easy on you so far, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:54.34,0:01:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This time around, you'll get no mercy!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:58.13,0:01:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn apes!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:59.55,0:02:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you what happens to guys who mess with our precious Mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:04.85,0:02:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, calm down, kiddo.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:06.77,0:02:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's been a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:10.94,0:02:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? B-Boss! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:13.69,0:02:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody kidnapped the girl. You couldn't be further from the truth.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:17.61,0:02:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.49,0:02:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,These two are head-over-heels for each other!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:24.04,0:02:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:24.95,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.21,0:02:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this true?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.76,0:02:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! And we've given them our blessing.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.10,0:02:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master! You've finally snagged yourself a girlfriend, eh?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.73,0:02:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man, we've been worried about you for the longest time!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:55.19,0:02:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Not having a single girlfriend at your age...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.15,0:03:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This calls for a celebration!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.45,0:03:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, hey... um...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.95,0:03:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.87,0:03:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:05.33,0:03:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown up, and I've failed to even notice!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.87,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Mistress, over the years I've guarded you, you've become a fine young lady!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.42,0:03:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be your Claude if I weren't overcome with joy!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.55,0:03:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... no... You were never "mine"...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.76,0:03:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This changes everything!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.39,0:03:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, Young Master, we'll gladly declare a ceasefire!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.18,0:03:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Same goes for us.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:29.64,0:03:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us throw our full support behind her, so that she may date him peacefully!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.90,0:03:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, hold up, you guys! Since when are we a couple?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I have to date this gorilla woman?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:39.53,0:03:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's right! Who'd want to date this bean sprout?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, punk.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.62,0:03:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I hear you wrong? You didn't really call our lady a gorilla woman, did you?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.96,0:03:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing to our Young Master?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you touch a single hair on his head, you're a dead man.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Young Master.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.55,0:04:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two... really boyfriend and girlfriend?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.30,0:04:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is bad.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.06,0:04:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What now? What do we do about this?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:12.14,0:04:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, playing along is our only option!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:15.86,0:04:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all or nothing now! We'll have to fake it!
