Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:16.73,Mikakunin,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\c&H141414&\fnFOT-Seurat Pro DB-Mikakunin\b9000\fscx150.01\fscy150.01\q2\pos(638.78,259.61)}It's all or nothing now! We'll have to fake it!
