Dialogue: 5,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.61,0:04:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we're totally hot for each other!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.45,0:04:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant that she's as strong and sweet as a gorilla!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.41,0:04:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to show you that our love isn't just {\i1}any{\i0} love.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, honey?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you go again, darling!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.71,0:04:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't confuse them like that!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.26,0:04:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course, that's what I love about you—your skin's as snow-white as a bean sprout!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.68,0:04:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My darling!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.10,0:04:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how 'bout that? So you two are head-over-heels in love, after all?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.53,0:05:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How did we end up like this?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.61,0:05:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see it's no use complaining?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:08.87,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we're getting out of this now.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:12.41,0:05:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we're a couple now, but what are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.67,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I've ever dated anyone before.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither have I, for your information. Not once!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.88,0:05:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, what can I say?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:27.68,0:05:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so good at things like romance.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.77,0:05:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for finding this, by the way.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.36,0:05:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've been awkward if we broke it off like that. That's all.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.07,0:05:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now you can go ahead and show me your eternal gratitude!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's the story?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.78,0:05:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it really seems important to you.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.95,0:05:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a keepsake from someone who died?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, someone gave it to me. A long time ago.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.08,0:05:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.71,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a kid... I was traveling overseas with my dad, and...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.72,0:06:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I got pretty close with this girl I met.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.01,0:06:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me, “We'll meet again,”
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.30,0:06:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and gave this to me as a token of our promise.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.81,0:06:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember her name or what she looked like.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:18.14,0:06:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All I remember is our promise.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.81,0:06:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm just hoping that if I hold onto it, we might actually meet again.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.23,0:06:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you hate me for that, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.24,0:06:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dwelling on the past and all...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.82,0:06:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What I hate is the kind of guy who keeps brooding over past mistakes
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.04,0:06:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and other things that he can't possibly change.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.41,0:06:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't say I hate romantic stories like yours.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.42,0:06:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we're gonna do something about this situation ASAP.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:47.05,0:06:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand the thought of dating you!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I could say the same, you moronic bean sprout!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.86,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master, you have a visitor!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Good mornin', Young Master.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:08.69,0:07:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,G'morning!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,G'morning!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning, darling!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.96,0:07:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to spring this on you,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but would you go on a date with me right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.31,Mikakunin,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\blur0.6\pos(914,522)\fscx130\fscy130\3c&H000000&\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\bord4\alpha&HA0&\t(755,800,\alpha&HA0&)}Episode 2: Encounter
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.31,Mikakunin,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\blur0.6\pos(909,517)\fscx130\fscy130\3c&HFFF6EF&\c&HFFF6EF&\1a&HFF&\bord4\t(755,800,\1a&H00&)}Episode 2: Encounter
Dialogue: 2,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.31,Mikakunin,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(800,0)\blur0.6\pos(909,517)\fscx130\fscy130\c&HFF7011&\3c&HFFF6EF&}Episode 2: Encounter
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.94,0:07:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A—
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.07,0:07:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A date?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.19,0:07:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should we?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you say?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.45,0:07:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's what couples do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.00,yryryr,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\c&H2E2E33&\fnYryr minc R\b1\fscx40\fscy45\pos(640,688)\frz2.3}Caution
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:04.75,yryryr,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\c&H6130F2&\org(53,157)\frz7.48\fscx45\fscy45\frx358\fry2\pos(350,197)}Beware of Stalkers
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.75,0:08:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, jeez, what have I done to deserve this?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not getting out of this, remember?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.22,0:08:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me, I don't have a clue!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:13.09,0:08:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it the guy's job to escort the girl around?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.68,0:08:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are thoughtless!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You really know how to piss someone off at every turn.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.43,0:08:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That said, I've never really gotten up close and personal with a girl, let alone gone on a date with one.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.27,0:08:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How should I know what to do on a date?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:29.69,0:08:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of all the dates with Onodera that I've fantasized about,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.11,0:08:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the ideal one had us sitting at a fashionable café and talking to each other,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.99,0:08:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then going to see a movie together,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}eating dinner together,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.62,0:08:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and finally taking a walk in a gorgeous park together.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}is{\i0} this? So gross!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.00,0:08:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of crappy beans are these? Are you all retarded?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! How can you live with yourselves, charging 600 yen for this!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.88,0:08:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Could this meat be any more rubbery?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.72,0:08:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Still tastes okay, though. One more, right now!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:09:01.10,Generic,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fnIwata New Gothic Pro E-CP\c&H3D32C6&\fscx50\fscy50\pos(668,146)}Truck\N Destroyer
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.89,0:09:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the commercial, and it has the mother of all explosion scenes! Looks rad!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we have to see this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:05.44,Generic,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fnIwata New Gothic Pro E-CP\c&HFCFFDE&\fscx50\fscy50\pos(694,276)\frz3.48\b1}Meow
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.89,0:09:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a four-handkerchief tearjerker and it's a current blockbuster!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.94,0:09:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess this is what couples usually watch.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's already asleep!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:16.70,0:09:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Despite everything...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even a girl like her...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.33,0:09:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}can look kind of cute when she's asleep.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.95,0:09:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as she's not talking or moving.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, just a tiny bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.22,0:09:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty. Go buy me some juice!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:37.22,0:09:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.26,0:09:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I take it back! She's not cute at all!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.43,0:09:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Yeah, you!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty cute!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:48.85,0:09:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you free? Wanna go to a café with us?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.82,0:09:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I happen to be waiting for someone right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.36,0:09:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, a bean sprout's technically a vegetable...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.57,0:10:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? You're funny, aren't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, just hang out with us, 'kay?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.83,0:10:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll show you a great time!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.71,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You ignoring us?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.42,0:10:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, we know you're alone.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Your boyfriend stand you up?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing! We'll take good care of you!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta say, you do have an amazing ass!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.59,0:10:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's turning me on!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:20.09,0:10:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you're half-Japanese, aren't you? Did your friends ditch you?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:23.47,0:10:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we get it. We get it.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:25.56,0:10:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, we'd never do that to you. You understand Japanese?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.73,0:10:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! Hello!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey! My apologies.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:35.44,0:10:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,See, she still doesn't understand a word of Japanese!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad. Sorry to keep you waiting, Kirisaki!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.99,0:10:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get out of here. This way, this way!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.12,0:10:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.75,0:10:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you stop me?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:55.59,0:10:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you trying to play the hero who saves the girl from the bad guys?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.67,0:11:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to break it to you, but in two seconds those guys could've been—
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the point!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to pick your battles! That's all!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.43,0:11:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea. I'm not defending those guys.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.73,0:11:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you whale on creeps who aren't even worth whaling on,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.65,0:11:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that's as good as admitting you're on their level!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.36,0:11:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be such a lame-ass!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.11,0:11:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What the... Who are you to talk to me like that?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.61,0:11:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell me! As if I'd ever give those guys the time of day!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It might have been for the briefest moment,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:28.95,0:11:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but for the first time in my life, I held hands with a girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.08,0:11:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for crying out loud.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.63,0:11:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it'd be like this! This date sucks!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only did you bore me to death, but you had to start lecturing me too!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about a buzz-kill.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.59,0:11:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Excuse{\i0} me?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.63,0:11:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.64,0:11:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't really call it the worst of the worst.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.22,0:11:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,On a scale of 1-100, today's date,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,after adding in double bonus points...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:53.19,0:11:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll give you a score of 1.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.32,0:12:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To the restroom. Don't ask why, retard!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For the first time in my life,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.66,0:12:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I let a guy lead me by the hand.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was so careless!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:10.91,0:12:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I really can't seem to figure her out. What's her deal?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.92,0:12:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:15.38,0:12:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man, if only I was on a date with Onodera!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.67,0:12:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That would totally be a dream come true!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.59,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say my name?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What a surprise!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:26.35,0:12:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw you and was about to say hi.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see me first?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.64,0:12:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,O... O...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.02,0:12:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Onodera!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.19,0:12:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here, Ichijou-kun?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.15,0:12:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What am {\i1}I{\i0} doing? What about yourself, Onodera?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.57,0:12:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? I just finished shopping with my friends so I'm on my way home.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is quite the surprise!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.54,0:12:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was about to say hi and surprise you,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but then all of a sudden, you said my name first!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, hey, I was just...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:00.75,0:13:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What... were you thinking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:04.68,0:13:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, something's off about them, you see?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.51,0:13:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I'm getting the same vibe.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.97,0:13:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of 'em are acting weird.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.52,0:13:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like there's no sign of them being all into each other like they were at the Yakuza's house..
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They're like an unnatural couple.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:18.56,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, they were arguing and all, which raises more suspicions.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}N-Not good...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.65,0:13:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.69,0:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have to do something, or all of today's suffering will have been for nothing!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.28,0:13:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time to really lay it on thick!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.95,0:13:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, darling! Thanks for being patient!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.58,0:13:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry! I took way longer than I thought.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.88,0:13:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ki... Kirisaki-san?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:47.38,0:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did she just call you... "darling"?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.06,0:13:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Um... Let's see...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.02,0:13:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's calling you darling, then that means...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.14,0:13:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are... uh... dating each other?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, no, no!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.56,0:14:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I be dating her?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.36,0:14:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's right! Who'd ever date him?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.40,0:14:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}N-No good!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.32,0:14:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone's...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.95,0:14:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}watching!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:08.95,0:14:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I don't want Onodera to think we're dating!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.45,0:14:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let that happen! But... what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.46,0:14:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:17.92,0:14:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.71,0:14:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We just started going out the other day!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, he's totally smitten with me!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}K-Kirisaki!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Play along with me!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:29.68,0:14:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's embarrassing in front of a classmate,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but what else can we do?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.27,0:14:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah! If it were just any classmate, I'd play the hell out of this role!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.73,0:14:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anybody but Onodera... Just not Onodera!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:41.94,0:14:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see. What a surprise. I had no idea!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.45,0:14:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}D-Damn it! What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.16,0:14:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Isn't that right, darling?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.28,0:14:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Who's smitten?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.29,0:14:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no clue what she's talking about!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.62,0:15:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! I just had a lovely dinner with my darling.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.34,0:15:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't my idea!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.42,0:15:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She insisted she wanted to eat meat!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.88,0:15:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you believe this boy? Every single weekend, he asks me to the movies.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.88,0:15:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I just happened to have tickets, that's all!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.22,0:15:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, I'm actually the type who prefers to go alone.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:14.10,0:15:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! I'm warning you, knock it off!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:15.26,0:15:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And anyway, this girl drools while she dozes off at the movies, you know!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.48,0:15:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.31,0:15:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered something I have to do! Gotta run, darling!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.07,0:15:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, Onodera!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, right.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want to let Kirisaki-san run off by herself?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:35.24,0:15:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's all right. I'll catch up soon enough.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything makes sense now.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.00,0:15:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although I wasn't able to trip them up today, I'm convinced now!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's definitely something fishy going on.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just you wait, you little scumbag twerp!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.26,0:15:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll personally crush any fly that gets near the Mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:54.51,0:15:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, listen, Onodera... We're...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.14,0:16:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really like that, okay? The truth is, we're not a coup—
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, Ichijou-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.56,0:16:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to say any more, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.07,0:16:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally understand.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't deny it, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.32,0:16:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're just hiding your embarrassment,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but you might hurt Kirisaki-san's feelings.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.95,0:16:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh... Hiding my embarrassment?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.79,0:16:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.66,0:16:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you two are perfect together!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.21,0:16:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so obvious that you're infatuated with each other!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.25,0:16:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}N-Not good! She's totally convinced that we're a couple!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:33.47,0:16:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are the gods subjecting me to such an ordeal?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.93,0:16:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry! You were in the middle of a date, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.76,0:16:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:39.93,0:16:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... No... Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:43.23,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.48,0:16:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now's the perfect chance. We're alone.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.36,0:16:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Onodera!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.57,0:16:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.07,0:16:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all right if I ask you just one question?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:04.12,0:17:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Have... Have you ever...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:06.79,0:17:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you'd ever seen this pendant before yesterday.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.71,0:17:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, maybe when you were little.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:24.81,0:17:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Never. Not once.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.27,0:17:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I have to go now, okay? You'd better not keep Kirisaki-san waiting,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichijou-kun!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.71,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I kept you waiting, Kirisaki!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.04,0:17:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you show your face, gutter-bug!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:50.54,0:17:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:53.01,0:17:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how humiliating that was?!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:57.05,0:18:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But you, on the other hand!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:57.68,0:18:00.05,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I know that, so just hear me out...
