Dialogue: 5,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.81,0:18:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a... um... you know!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:08.35,0:18:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My way of apologizing.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... I screwed up.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.11,0:18:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're more straightforward than you look.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.57,0:18:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What is this, anyway?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.41,0:18:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, it's called a dorayaki.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.33,0:18:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't taste like the ones from my favorite shop,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but trust me, it's still pretty awesome. Try one!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:29.29,0:18:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate it.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:40.05,0:18:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.80,0:18:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Kosaki!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.93,0:18:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I used a new recipe for these dorayaki. Do you want to try one?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:46.68,0:18:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I think I'll pass. I'll be in my room.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:04.20,0:19:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do now?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.37,0:19:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I lied to him.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:12.21,0:19:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.21,0:19:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Asking him will be all the more difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:20.12,Mikakunin,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\pos(640,310)\c&H350BE2&}Ichijou-kun is this type of person
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:24.10,Mikakunin,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\pos(640,310)\c&H350BE2&}Ichijou-kun is this type of person
Dialogue: 5,0:19:24.60,0:19:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together on animal care duty.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.93,0:19:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been taking care of all these animals by yourself?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:32.73,0:19:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to say, you didn't do half bad, considering how many there are.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.73,0:19:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No sweat! They're practically family to me!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.53,0:19:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you've been waiting for this. Chow time!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How 'bout it? Looks yummy, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:48.87,0:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are such a helpless bunch!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:51.42,0:19:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks more like they hate you.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.08,0:19:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.84,0:19:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly how many animals do you have here?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:58.96,0:20:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,About ninety, if I had to say?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninety?! Is this a zoo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.84,0:20:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So like, do they all have names?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:06.05,0:20:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, some of them. I've only decided on half, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:09.14,0:20:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Only half?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.35,0:20:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought they were your family.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.35,0:20:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How naïve. It's precisely because they're family!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.31,0:20:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Naming them is a very delicate process!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:21.07,0:20:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Divine Spacer Kuniyoshi?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:28.87,Mikakunin,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\pos(640,310)\c&H350BE2&}Kirisaki-san is this type of person
Dialogue: 5,0:20:28.87,0:20:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try naming them, then?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come up with anything funny, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Name them?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:34.88,0:20:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I could.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, this little one is...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:40.42,0:20:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably Number One.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:41.84,0:20:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That one is Number Two.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is Number Three.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:44.34,0:20:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one here...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:46.09,0:20:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, forget it.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:47.22,0:20:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, since you're also in charge of raising them,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:50.27,0:20:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,at least get to know the ones that already have names.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:53.85,0:20:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, this is Rodriguez IV, the turtle.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:57.61,0:21:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I wonder how he'd taste grilled.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:00.78,0:21:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And this chicken is Kato the Crusher.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:03.11,0:21:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Which parts are the juiciest?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:08.07,0:21:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
